{"tid":2450230,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國運輸部警告或限制香港航空公司在美營運航班","createTime":"2021-03-17T08:42:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T14:26:36.000Z","uid":291865,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"acd78c2a5bcf9667b8b63b6bd9715daacc269bd7","tid":2450230,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:42:50.000Z","msg":"美國運輸部警告或限制香港航空公司在美營運航班<br />\n<br />\n美國運輸部警告，可能會限制香港的航空公司，在美國營運航班，回應香港收緊對機組人員的檢疫安排。 美國運輸部發布命令，要求總部設在香港的國泰航空，7日內提交所有在美國營運航班的資料，以審視有無違反法律，或對公眾利益構成不利影響。運輸部認為，新的檢疫安排影響美國聯邦快遞FedEx的業務，為FedEx帶來龐大的營運成本，但香港當局同時容許以封閉方式，停留美國阿拉斯加安克雷奇的國泰貨機機組人員，只須接受醫學監察，認為措施令香港的航空公司受益，損害美國航空公司的營運權利。FedEx表示，希望有關命令有助解決事件，並正與美國和香港當局合作。國泰暫時未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n2021-03-17 16:34:13<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581087-20210317.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581087-20210317.htm&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CTwQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=1e049020\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581087-20210317.htm&h=06b7acf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581087-20210317.htm</a>"},{"pid":"72d3527adeccaea0b44845cf5e0b611000ac20a7","tid":2450230,"uid":155095,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:43:35.000Z","msg":"香港以後做大灣區直航呀，唔稀罕你美國呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e6ba8ece2c5557be4b5109fefc561622f41d23","tid":2450230,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T09:03:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53dbe4108ccf618c019a52d7b376